I spent *all* of last weekend, save a couple of hours, in Lower Guk, including one night where I and a full group of 50+ folks completely raped the place, and I guess I don't have to mention that the Sage once again did not drop a Runed Cowl (oh, but he did in the 3 hours I was out of the dungeon, naturally).  I did manage to get a backpack plus of cinch cords, which I have been distributing to young casters in the Oasis, and 2 levels (sadly, Lguk is light blueing and greening out now), plus plenty of other assorted crap, so my lower level guild members all got presents this weekend, but I am at the point of admitting defeat.  Fifteen levels is enough, and besides, I am going to have to come back and camp yet again for his friend the Scribe, and for my SMR, before too much longer, and I am beginning to think he has it in for me...<br>
<br>
I started this post thinking that I was going to end it by asking if anyone had one of these godforsaken things for sale, but at this point, I don't think I even want to *see* one; it would make me too irritated.  So I guess I can live with 191 (buffed) Int for a few more levels... <br>
